The paper focuses on providing a system for measuring energy consumption in mobile applications, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and mobile computing (cs.MOBILE). The system combines energy models and hardware-based measurements, which involves system-level programming (cs.SY) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper also discusses the need for continuous data to build energy models, which relates to data-centric computing (cs.DC).
